Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:29.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4.533}咲き乱れゆく青い花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:34.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4.533}愛に怯え　揺れる果実
